Feedback.remarks: I think this is a great idea - you used to be able to go to a rental store and ask for a recommendation, but these days there's so many options it's difficult to find something you really want to watch. There are thousands of movies on streaming services like Netflix, and it can be overwhelming. So I really like the concept.
